        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-accent mb-2">Summary</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 text-muted font-body">The phrase ‘The Venus Project’ refers to a 501(c)3 organization and its emerging collective body of work but carries additional meanings which include:</p>
